[
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說鹹水喻經",
        "from": "T01n0029_001:0811b01_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "失譯人名今附西晉錄",
        "from": "T01n0029_001:0811b03_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "聞如是：一時，婆伽婆在舍衛城祇樹給孤獨",
        "from": "T01n0029_001:0811b04_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "園。",
        "from": "T01n0029_001:0811b05_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時世尊告諸比丘：",
        "from": "T01n0029_001:0811b05_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我與汝等說水喻七事，諦聽諦思念之，我當說。",
        "from": "T01n0029_001:0811b06_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」對曰：",
        "from": "T01n0029_001:0811b06_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如是，世尊！",
        "from": "T01n0029_001:0811b06_23",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時諸比丘從佛聞教。",
        "from": "T01n0029_001:0811b07_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊告曰：",
        "from": "T01n0029_001:0811b07_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「云何，比丘！",
        "from": "T01n0029_001:0811b07_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "水喻七事？",
        "from": "T01n0029_001:0811b08_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若人沒於水；",
        "from": "T01n0029_001:0811b08_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "從水出頭復還沒水；",
        "from": "T01n0029_001:0811b08_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或出頭遍觀四方；",
        "from": "T01n0029_001:0811b09_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或出頭不復沒水；",
        "from": "T01n0029_001:0811b09_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或有人欲行出水；",
        "from": "T01n0029_001:0811b10_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或有人欲至彼岸；",
        "from": "T01n0029_001:0811b10_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或有人已至彼岸，淨志得立彼岸。",
        "from": "T01n0029_001:0811b11_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「彼云何人沒溺於水？",
        "from": "T01n0029_001:0811b11_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或有一人以不善法盡纏裹身，純罪熟，至地獄一劫受罪不可療治，是謂此人常沒溺於水，是謂初入水沒溺。",
        "from": "T01n0029_001:0811b14_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「彼云何人出頭還沒入水？",
        "from": "T01n0029_001:0811b14_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或有一人作是沒溺，有信於善法，懷慙愧，求其方便，於諸善法皆懷慙愧，彼出於水還沒溺水，是謂二人沒溺於水。",
        "from": "T01n0029_001:0811b17_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「彼云何人出水遍觀四方？",
        "from": "T01n0029_001:0811b18_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或有一人出水，彼有信於善法，有慙愧心，有勇猛意，於諸不善法皆有慙愧。",
        "from": "T01n0029_001:0811b19_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼出水上，不復沒溺於水。",
        "from": "T01n0029_001:0811b20_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此諸賢，是謂三人喻彼出水。",
        "from": "T01n0029_001:0811b21_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「彼云何人出水住？",
        "from": "T01n0029_001:0811b21_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或有一人作是出水，有信於善法，有慙愧，有精進，於諸善法皆懷慙愧，彼於三結使盡，成須陀洹而不退轉，必當還所獲，是謂四人喻彼出水住。",
        "from": "T01n0029_001:0811b24_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「彼云何人出水欲至彼岸？",
        "from": "T01n0029_001:0811b25_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或有一人作如是出水，彼有信於善法，有慙愧，有勇猛意，於諸善法悉懷慙愧，彼盡三結使，貪欲、瞋恚、愚癡薄，成斯陀含，來至此間而盡苦本，是謂彼人喻彼水欲至彼岸。",
        "from": "T01n0029_001:0811b29_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「云何彼人已至彼岸？",
        "from": "T01n0029_001:0811b29_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或有一人便出水，有信於善法，有慙愧，有勇猛意，於諸善法皆懷慙愧，彼便盡五下分結，成阿那含，於彼般涅槃，不復來至此間，是謂六人喻彼出水已至彼岸。",
        "from": "T01n0029_001:0811c04_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「彼云何人已至彼岸，淨志得立彼岸？",
        "from": "T01n0029_001:0811c05_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或有一人而出水上，有信於善法，有慙愧，有勇猛意，於諸善法皆懷慙愧；",
        "from": "T01n0029_001:0811c06_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "或有一人盡有漏成無漏，念解脫、智慧解脫，於現法中疾得證通，而自娛樂盡生死源。",
        "from": "T01n0029_001:0811c08_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "梵行已立，所作已辦，更不復受母胎。",
        "from": "T01n0029_001:0811c09_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是謂彼人喻彼水已立彼出岸。",
        "from": "T01n0029_001:0811c10_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「如是，比丘！",
        "from": "T01n0029_001:0811c10_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此七人，我今與汝等說七人喻水。",
        "from": "T01n0029_001:0811c11_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "諸世尊與諸聲聞所應當說，有大慈，欲使獲安隱，皆使得度，所謂閑居處、樹下、空處露坐，汝等坐禪勿有懈怠；",
        "from": "T01n0029_001:0811c13_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "今不精勤後備有悔。",
        "from": "T01n0029_001:0811c14_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是謂我所教勅。",
        "from": "T01n0029_001:0811c14_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」爾時諸比丘聞佛所說，歡喜奉行。",
        "from": "T01n0029_001:0811c15_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說鹹水喻經",
        "from": "T01n0029_001:0811c16_100",
        "context_with_next_sentence": false
    }
]